'''西蒙·理察·確斯'''（{{lang-en|Simon Richard Cox}}，{{bd|1987年|4月28日|catidx=Cox, Simon}}），出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[伯克郡|伯克郡]]的[[雷丁|雷丁]]，[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現效力[[澳大利亞職業足球聯賽|澳大利亞職業足球聯賽]]球隊[[西悉尼流浪者足球俱樂部|西悉尼流浪者]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 早期 ===
確斯在[[雷丁|雷丁]]郊區小鎮蒂莱霍斯特（Tilehurst）出生，於年僅8歲時被[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]教練凯文·狄龙（Kevin Dillon）發掘及羅致旗下<small><ref name=rfccontract>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~743344,00.html |title=Reading-born Academy forward Simon Cox signs first professional contract |work=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |date=2005-11-18 |accessdate=2009-05-15 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref></small>。

=== 雷丁 ===
2005年9月20日確斯首次為[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]一隊上陣，在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]主場1-0擊敗[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]，於完場前後補登場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/4258492.stm |title=Reading 1-0 Luton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-09-20 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2018-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617144847/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/4258492.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在為一隊在聯賽盃後補上陣兩場後，已屆18歲的確斯於11月18日簽署首份[[職業|職業]]合約，留效直到2007年夏季<small><ref name=rfccontract/></small>。在球季結束前再獲機會在兩場[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]及兩場[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|聯賽]]後補上陣。

[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]雷丁升級到[[英超|英超]]作賽，確斯未能在一隊佔一席位，於2006年9月11日獲外借到[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球會[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|賓福特]]1個月汲取上陣經驗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brentford/5334580.stm |title=Reading teenager joins Brentford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-09-11 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307195114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brentford/5334580.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，他獲派5次上陣，包括4場聯賽及1場[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]，但不幸於9月26日對陣[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]時斷腳，[[腓骨|腓骨]]有裂痕而預計需養傷1個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brentford/5385210.stm |title=Double injury blow hits Brentford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-09-27 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306235644/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brentford/5385210.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，確斯提前結束外借返回雷丁<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~903968,00.html |title=Royals youngster Cox suffers broken leg while playing on loan at Brentford |work=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |date=2006-09-27 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080210152811/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~903968%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-02-10 }}</ref></small>。腳傷痊癒後確斯先在預備隊上陣兩場後，於11月22日再次返回賓福特協助球隊保級<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~932071,00.html |title=Cox joins Brentford on loan |work=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |date=2006-11-22 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080210152816/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~932071%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-02-10 }}</ref></small>，外借期直到2007年1月8日才結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brentford/6174118.stm |title=Reading's Cox rejoins Brentford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-22 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308191721/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/brentford/6174118.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，期間上陣9場。回到雷丁後，於1月27日在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]作客3-2淘汰[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]，確斯於下半場後補入替入球功臣之一的[[戴夫·傑臣|戴夫·傑臣]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6282157.stm |title=Birmingham 2-3 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-27 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226230258/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/6282157.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。3月22日確斯一季內第三次外借，加盟另一支[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球會[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|諾咸頓]]，為期1個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/northampton_town/6481135.stm |title=Northampton land Reading striker |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-22 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307144630/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/northampton_town/6481135.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，隊中還有另一名由雷丁外借的隊友[[阿列克斯·皮尔斯|阿列克斯·皮尔斯]]（Alex Pearce）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1000532,00.html |title=Cox and Henry complete loan moves |work=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |date=2007-03-22 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080210152739/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~1000532%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-02-10 }}</ref></small>，4月7日作客2-0擊敗[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]，確斯於12分鐘首開紀錄射入處子入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6513451.stm |title=Leyton Orient 0-2 Northampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-04-07 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310075747/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6513451.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；4月14日作客[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，確斯再次先拔頭籌，但最終1-4敗陣而回<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6534655.stm |title=Blackpool 4-1 Northampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-04-14 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2012-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112030412/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6534655.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；4月21日主場對[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|車士打菲特]]，確斯一箭定江山<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6555299.stm |title=Northampton 1-0 Chesterfield |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-04-21 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307081932/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6555299.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；在4場比賽射入3球後，諾咸頓與雷丁協議延長借用直到球季結束，參與餘下的兩輪比賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/northampton_town/6595347.stm |title=Reading's Cox stays with Cobblers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-04-26 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307092638/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/northampton_town/6595347.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2007年7月4日確斯續簽一年新約，留隊直到[[2007年至2008年英格蘭超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1067116,00.html |title=Four new contracts agreed |publisher=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |date=2007-07-04 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411130459/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~1067116%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-04-11 }}</ref></small>。雷丁在季前到[[南韓|南韓]]參加兩年一度的[[和平盃足球賽|和平盃]]（Peace Cup），7月16日分組賽第二場對[[法甲|法甲]]五連冠[[里昂足球會|里昂]]，確斯獲派正選上陣，更在下半場62分鐘一箭定江山，協助球隊小勝最終奪冠的里昂1-0<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/peacecup07.html |title=Peace Cup 2007 |publisher=RSSSF |date=2008-07-03 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2018-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030185848/http://www.rsssf.com/tablesp/peacecup07.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。8月28日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]第二圈作客對[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]，確斯於[[加時賽|加時]]後補入替，最終1-0險勝過關<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/6963517.stm |title=Swansea 0-1 Reading (aet) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-28 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2020-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004042359/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/6963517.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。8月31日確斯再被外借到[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球會[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]，為期6個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/6973434.stm |title=Swindon boss seals triple swoop |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-01 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307010637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/6973434.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。9月4日首場上陣對[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|賓福特]]即射入一球，協助球隊大勝4-1在[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|聯賽錦標]]晉級第二圈<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/6973865.stm |title=Swindon 4-1 Brentford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-04 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2017-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222054044/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/6973865.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；確斯延續其上季尾的入球氣勢，在外借期間上陣21場，合共射入9球，包括在10月6日對[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|基寧咸]]射入兩球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7019637.stm |title=Swindon 5-0 Gillingham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-06 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307110736/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7019637.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。借用期滿確斯返回雷丁，於2008年1月15日[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第三圈重賽主場出戰[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7184872.stm |title=Reading 0-1 Tottenham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-15 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2008-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080119075215/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7184872.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，新任[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]主帥[[法比奥·卡佩罗|卡比路]]亦在座，落後0-1的雷丁於半場調入確斯取代首次正選上陣的[[後衛_(足球)|中堅]]阿列克斯·皮尔斯，確斯擔任[[中場|右翼]]加強攻力，雖然未能平反敗局，賽後仍然獲得領隊[[斯蒂夫·科贝尔|郭甫]]的稱讚<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10306~1216505,00.html |title=Verdict on Federici, Cox, Pearce & Lita |publisher=[[雷丁足球俱乐部|''readingfc.co.uk'']] |date=2008-01-16 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080117030212/http://www.readingfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0%2C%2C10306~1216505%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-01-17 }}</ref></small>。

=== 史雲頓 ===
2008年1月31日轉會窗關閉前，確斯終於與[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]達成個人薪酬協議，簽約兩年半<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7219857.stm |title=Swindon sign Reading striker Cox |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-31 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017001405/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7219857.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，轉會費金額沒有透露，據報超過20萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，加盟後確斯表示希望在餘下球季再射入6球，達到其個人目標的每季15球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7234977.stm |title=Striker Cox seeks six more goals |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-08 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307190159/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7234977.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。5月4日聯賽煞科日主場2-1擊敗[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]，確斯射入一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7368714.stm |title=Swindon 2-1 Millwall |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-15 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402163132/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7368714.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，是他正式加盟後的第六球，亦剛好達到他每季射入15球的目標。

[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]到[[奧地利|奧地利]]作季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7497957.stm |title=Swindon in Austria for pre-season |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-09 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307070912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7497957.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，2008年7月11日首場對[[布加勒斯特星隊|布加勒斯特星隊]]，確斯射入一球，雙方2-2平手完場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7502575.stm |title=We learned from Steaua - Malpas |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-11 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307082020/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7502575.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；7月14日次場對應屆[[歐聯|歐聯]]八強[[土耳其|土耳其]]的[[费内巴切体育俱乐部|費倫巴治]]，[[马特亚·凯日曼|基士文]]為費倫巴治先拔頭籌，確斯25碼外「窩利」射入扳平1-1，兩戰入兩球，而史雲頓亦保持不敗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7504977.stm |title=Cox on target in Fenerbahce draw |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-14 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307215047/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7504977.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。開季前確斯為手部一塊碎骨進行[[手術|手術]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7528495.stm |title=Swindon hit by Amankwaah injury |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-28 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307143229/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7528495.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]確斯大爆發，效力[[斯温登足球俱乐部|史雲頓]]首個完整球季，在各項比賽合共射入32球，比季前預測的25球還要多<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7539906.stm |title=Striker Cox has lofty ambitions |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-07 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307062615/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7539906.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其中29個聯賽入球是球隊總入球68球的4成有多，使他與[[布里斯托流浪足球俱乐部|布里斯托流浪]]的[[瑞奇·兰伯特|瑞奇·兰伯特]]併列[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]首席射手。2009年1月27日主場3-2擊敗[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|華素爾]]，為新任領隊[[丹尼·威爾遜|丹尼·威爾遜]]（Danny Wilson）帶來首場勝仗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7847270.stm |title=Swindon 3-2 Walsall |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307202222/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7847270.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，確斯25碼的「笠」射被譽為有[[丹尼斯·博格坎普|柏金]]的入球風格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7856012.stm |title=Wilson hails 'classic' Cox goal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-28 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310123632/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7856012.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季內確斯三次造出[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，均為作客比賽，分別為2008年10月3日3-3賽和[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特普爾]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7639299.stm |title=Hartlepool 3-3 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-03 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2018-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016032844/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7639299.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>、11月1日3-3賽和[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7686103.stm |title=Scunthorpe 3-3 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-01 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2018-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016081400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7686103.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>及2009年3月24日4-3擊敗[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|諾咸頓]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7948790.stm |title=Northampton 3-4 Swindon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-24 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2018-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016081358/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7948790.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。確斯出色的表現使他獲選10月份「[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]每月最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7948790.stm |title=Swindon's Cox wins monthly award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-04 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2018-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016081358/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7948790.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。 

史雲頓警告其他球會不要打確斯主意，仍然有一年合約在身的確斯，在簽約時未足21歲，就算約滿後轉會，史雲頓仍可收取補償金，史雲頓為確斯估值超過100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7978754.stm |title=Swindon value striker at over £1m |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-02 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217225342/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/7978754.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但球季結束後不絕的轉會傳聞亦迫令史雲頓作出打算<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8040244.stm |title=Swindon prepared for Cox offers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-08 |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217231610/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swindon_town/8040244.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，史雲頓亦拒絕了重返[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]的[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]及[[蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|蘇超]]領頭羊[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]的收購要求<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2009-05-14 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8048694.stm |title=Swindon reject two bids for Cox |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2009-05-15 |archive-date=2009-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090522114543/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/8048694.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

